						<div class="content">
							<h3> Smoke and Mirrors </h3>
							<p> <b> <i> Pathways </i> </b> </p>
							<p> There were so many paths I could have taken in my life. Like the one that ran by the riverbank, where wild roses grew with sharp thorns. Or perhaps I should have followed my instincs and explored the track that wound its way through a dark and mysterious forest. </p>
							<p> However, I ended up choosing the path of least resistance. The one that looked the easiest. Only to discover it was made of quicksand. </p>
					</div>
